<h2 class="centrify mb-4">API Example</h2>

<h5>To get results in JSON format, you can visit:</h5>
<%= simple_format <<~EOF
		#{link_to render_results_url(5), render_results_path(5)}
		Or
		#{link_to render_results2_url(5), render_results2_url(5) }

	EOF
%>

<h5><p>For example, in a sample ruby program:</p></h5>
<pre class="code">
<%= example_code(render_results_url(rand(5..10))) %>
</pre>

The value specifies the value of Pi.
The time specifies the time the server spent calculating Pi!
